    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>lamb meatballs</strong> and cook for an initial 5-6 min or until starting to brown all over</p><p>Once brown, transfer the <strong>meatballs</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1683046811150-x200.jpg",
