            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683046832163-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>lamb meatball biryani </strong>with the <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>minty mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
